title Directions - Use Case Diagram

actor Customer
actor FOHStaff
actor Chef
actor Deliverer

rectangle System {
FOHStaff --> (Open Deliveroo for business day)
Customer --> (Enter details into app)
Customer --> (Look for nearby restaurants)
Customer --> (Order food from app)
Customer --> (Pay for food)
FOHStaff --> (Receive order via alert)
Chef --> (Prepare order)
Chef --> (Alert FOH staff when order ready)
FOHStaff --> (Pack for delivery)
Deliverer --> (Collect for delivery)
Deliverer --> (Deliver order)
Customer --> (Receive order)
}

